## How-to-setup

* Sign in to [GCS](https://shell.cloud.google.com/?show=terminal)
* Run the below command
```bash
  git clone https://github.com/itzdarklucifer/xRDP && cd xRDP && chmod +x xRDP.sh && ./xRDP.sh
```
